Things to include

PERSONAL
    Avatar?
    year of birth
    email (create user for online deletion)
    password
    discrete mode
    sync?

GENERAL
    Turn on/off notification
    Snooze notification
    Sign out
    Invite/share (choose method by OS default alternatives)
    About
